issues.title: Bounding box jitter in high-density retail zones
issues.description: Bounding boxes exhibit jittering during peak hours in high-density zones. Investigate temporal smoothing and Kalman filter parameter adjustments.

issues.title: Thermal imaging overexposure in bright environments
issues.description: Safety analysis module fails to detect objects accurately in environments with excessive thermal contrast. Fine-tune exposure calibration.

commits.message: Added temporal smoothing for bounding box jitter in retail zones.
Adjusted exposure calibration for bright environments in safety analysis.

issues.title: Failure in parallel processing for large video datasets
issues.description: Deepfake detection module crashes when processing large datasets in parallel. Investigate thread allocation and memory usage.

issues.title: Inconsistent frame alignment during preprocessing
issues.description: Deepfake detection preprocessing pipeline occasionally misaligns video frames, causing downstream model failures. Validate and optimize alignment module.

commits.message: Optimized thread allocation for parallel processing in large datasets.
Resolved frame alignment issues in preprocessing pipeline.

issues.title: Occlusion failures for suburban crosswalks
issues.description: Person detection in autonomous vehicles struggles with partial occlusions at suburban crosswalks during low light conditions.

issues.title: Latency spike during multi-angle camera integration
issues.description: Integrating multi-angle cameras in autonomous vehicles increases latency by 25%. Profile and optimize synchronization logic.

commits.message: Enhanced training dataset for suburban crosswalk occlusions.
Optimized synchronization logic for multi-angle camera latency.
